1. Module Purpose

The Savings Scheme Module manages recurring jewellery savings plans offered to customers.

Customers deposit a fixed monthly amount and receive benefits such as bonus installments, discounts, or redemption privileges at maturity.

Responsibilities:

* Scheme Configuration
* Customer Enrollment
* Monthly Deposits
* Missed Installment Tracking
* Maturity Calculation
* Bonus Calculation
* Redemption Management
* Scheme Ledger
* Notifications
* Scheme Analytics

