7. Core Business Rules

BR-SCH-001

Customer required for enrollment.

BR-SCH-002

Scheme cannot start without first installment.

BR-SCH-003

Installments immutable after posting.

BR-SCH-004

Matured schemes cannot accept deposits.

BR-SCH-005

Redemption allowed only after maturity.

BR-SCH-006

Bonus rules determined by scheme configuration.

BR-SCH-007

Every deposit generates receipt.

BR-SCH-008

Scheme ledger is immutable.

