⸻

11. Maturity Engine

Purpose

Calculate maturity benefits.

⸻

Formula

Maturity Value:

Maturity\ Value = Deposits + Bonus

⸻

Example

Monthly Installment = ₹5,000
Duration = 11 Months
Bonus = ₹5,000

⸻

Result

Maturity Value = ₹60,000

